{"tid":1023280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救🆘老母幫人幫到眾叛親離","createTime":"2019-02-15T15:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T16:31:56.000Z","uid":236876,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b433767a8b8e099cee87a262720f379eab222e62","tid":1023280,"uid":236876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"有啲野關於我老母嘅，想各位巴打絲打出下主意，主持公道！<br />\n是咁的，我老母有個識咗廿幾年嘅on9 fd，近一兩年患咗抑鬱症，夜晚瞓教好想人哋陪住佢，所以就叫我老母喺佢屋企陪佢瞓！瞓咗幾日我都覺得可以嘅，但係條友越嚟越過分，由原本一個禮拜一兩日變咗起碼三四日。要我老母喺佢屋企訓都算，佢每個禮拜六日都拉我老母陪佢食飯行街。本身老母都要返工，而家星期六日都唔係屋企，搞到成班屋企人幾乎冇見過佢咁滯。<br />\n正所謂近朱者赤，近墨者黑。個on9 fd本身好暴躁，又成日講粗口，又大洗。最近我老母都開始學埋佢啲衰嘢，去餐廳亂鬧侍應，之後又月洗五萬蚊，洗撚晒我同阿哥啲錢。<br />\n條On9 fd係IT狗，依家叫我老母拎晒啲積蓄去買礦機俾佢托管，而家已經俾咗四十萬！點先可以叫老母同條pk斷絕關係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df04a8124a9732a24be68d2eb808c55a045df0e","tid":1023280,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"肯定只係朋友？"},{"pid":"b987eab1a84108a02561d6cd4a9c075b24498c45","tid":1023280,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"你老母個fd係男定女？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d938549f16728cf2d3e9ed3cda392a53bc98dfa8","tid":1023280,"uid":110672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"過來人 搬走 臨走前講返聲<br />\n我會記得有個老母生我出黎<br />\n電話改尻埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03afe5ea8dd7308761d26564cc8812e68f015038","tid":1023280,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"扮抑鬱鑿到人哋幾廿萬<br />\n新招嚟，有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa9712d06d69b98e188d151499ab995cdbe92f3","tid":1023280,"uid":236876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"宜家個on9 fd冇撚端端生濕疹，DLLM自己搞唔掂又叫我老母幫佢搞。老母日日都要去佢屋企幫佢整面，晚晚搞到12點先返屋企，平時放工放假都要去！而家佢癲到放工都直接去人屋企，屋企都唔番，飯又唔煮，搞到我地要成日食外賣，前排我仲腸胃炎🤮老母返到嚟屋企淨係識講電話，我地做漏少少家務都喺度屌到我哋飛起。依家我哋每日見老母都唔多個三個鐘，究竟佢當我地係屋企人定係當佢pk fd係屋企人？！"},{"pid":"8752cc345222c4fe392797cbc4494725dfef827f","tid":1023280,"uid":236876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b987eab1a84108a02561d6cd4a9c075b24498c45","tid":1023280,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"你老母個fd係男定女？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:11:00.000Z","msg":"女"},{"pid":"495574dc7341b0b752c44bb536d0e639e9a77cc5","tid":1023280,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"你老豆點講？"},{"pid":"a5893aa397a560232c1b9553b4ae387cfa99e045","tid":1023280,"uid":236876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"495574dc7341b0b752c44bb536d0e639e9a77cc5","tid":1023280,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"你老豆點講？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"十歲嗰陣老豆死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1428a80d72204f35664b2f2173cf430d6431426b","tid":1023280,"uid":125388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"sheshe? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5059d8faf73d7435f88766a5b6f4c0e7fbbcd6cf","tid":1023280,"uid":236401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09337428757a4e7bab612bb0b4bf8ad70347caa2","tid":1023280,"uid":236401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef34abd471af3278d592d079f3add6b3c8ef0929","tid":1023280,"uid":236876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"認真！有冇解決方法？🙏🏻"},{"pid":"f5069c21b1aaaeade6c56b1611e1272e1172e2e2","tid":1023280,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:29:09.000Z","msg":"而家先掘礦會唔會遲咗d？<br />\n<br />\n定係上咗幣少隻賊船？"},{"pid":"1661c8b6d6a2a0f7db6e4d93ccbab4fd99b8422e","tid":1023280,"uid":162713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:31:56.000Z","msg":"你同你阿哥再喊曬口<br />\n<br />\n話唔想好似而家無左老母咁<br />\n<br />\n唔得 再換鎖<br />\n<br />\n嚇一嚇佢<br />\n<br />\n最後手段 同阿哥一齊搬走<br />\n<br />\n如果 以上三招做曬都無用<br />\n<br />\n就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}